skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: state college vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in and around State College, Pennsylvania. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable State College Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask State College Vegan for a fact."
